# The compatibility libraries in this folder are committed to the repo so it is
# fully self-contained — a fresh clone can build and run with no extra steps.
#
# These are open-source Loki-era shared libraries (SDL 1.2, smpeg, smjpeg,
# FreeType/ttf, libstdc++ from the GCC 2.95 / egcs era — all LGPL/GPL). They are
# NOT Tribes 2 game data, so redistributing them here is fine.
#
# Only ignore transient build artifacts.
*.o
